edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan

Class SortNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan.PlanNode
      • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan.PlanNode.Unary
        • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan.SortNode

  • public class SortNode
extends PlanNode.Unary
    A concrete implementation of a relational plan operator representing an ORDER BY clause. Defined in terms of a list of SortNode.Ordering instances that contain an Expression (what to sort by) and a boolean for ascending/descending.
